          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A shadow skims over your head, and you duck, thinking you\u2019re about\nto be attacked by a hungry irix. You look up in relief to see the shape\nof Ben Amon\u2019s custom-made glider, the Swift, passing overhead. It\nlands gently in a clearing a short distance away. As you approach, you\nsee Ben Amon emerge from the cockpit, stretch his legs, then check\nsomething on the underside of the vehicle."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"Hello there!\" he says, looking up from his work. \"I'm on an errand\nfor Elder Thrush, but if you're in need of assistance, maybe I can give\nyou a ride.\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
